<plot>This documentary traces the 75 year history of the ANC in unusually candid interviews, some shot secretly inside South Africa. President Oliver Tambo, Albertina Sisulu, Thabo Mbeki and Military Chief Joe Slovo discuss the ANC's history, its political and military strategy and its long-term goals.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?509542</url></doc>
